title.narrative: Expanded Comprehensive Response to HIV/AIDS in Timor-Leste

description.narrative: Timor-Leste - HIV - Ministry of Health of the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste - MOH. This program has the following goals: Reducing STI and HIV/AIDS mortality and morbidity in Timor-Leste by enhancing related prevention and treatment services. The objectives of this program are: Strengthen and expand HTC and access to HIV and AIDS treatment and care (objective 2). Strengthen strategic information systems to enable an appropriate level of response to the HIV epidemic (objective 3). Expansion of community based HIV prevention and HIV testing programs for key populations (objective 1)
